.DT
offer
$MUDNAME$ player help
offer

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
offer - Offer an object for sale to another player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
offer <object> to <player> for <money>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This will offer an object for sale to another player.  The offer will be
handled securely, so that the hand over of the object and the money
will happen with no loss.

The other player must then accept the transaction for it to successfully
go through.  You can withdraw the transaction before it is completed if
you do not wish to continue to offer the items for sale.
.EP

.SH Examples:
.SI 5
> offer book to vixen for 20 platinum
> offer book to vixen for 20 gold
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
accept, give, withdraw.
.EP
